statements: SELECT * FROM diversity_reports ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT report_id, initiative_name FROM diversity_reports WHERE impact_score > 50;
SELECT initiative_name, cultural_changes FROM diversity_reports WHERE report_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT report_id, initiative_name, cultural_changes FROM diversity_reports WHERE impact_score < 30 ORDER BY initiative_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM diversity_reports WHERE cultural_changes IS NOT NULL AND impact_score BETWEEN 40 AND 60 ORDER BY report_id DESC;
SELECT initiative_name, impact_score FROM diversity_reports WHERE report_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM diversity_reports WHERE impact_score > 50 ORDER BY impact_score DESC;
SELECT initiative_name, impact_score, report_date FROM diversity_reports ORDER BY report_date ASC, impact_score DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT DISTINCT initiative_name FROM diversity_reports WHERE impact_score BETWEEN 40 AND 60;
SELECT * FROM diversity_reports WHERE initiative_name LIKE 'Diversity%' ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM diversity_report;
SELECT report_title, report_date FROM diversity_report ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT impact_rating, report_title FROM diversity_report WHERE impact_rating > 3;
SELECT * FROM initiative_details ORDER BY initiative_start_date ASC;
SELECT initiative_name, initiative_type FROM initiative_details WHERE initiative_type = 'Diversity Initiative';
SELECT report_title FROM diversity_report WHERE report_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM initiative_details WHERE initiative_type = 'Training' ORDER BY initiative_start_date DESC;
SELECT report_title, impact_rating FROM diversity_report WHERE impact_rating > 3 ORDER BY impact_rating ASC, report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM diversity_report JOIN initiative_details ON diversity_report.report_id = initiative_details.initiative_id;
SELECT initiative_name, initiative_type FROM initiative_details WHERE initiative_start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';

SELECT initiative_name, start_date, end_date FROM diversity_initiatives;
SELECT id, initiative_name FROM diversity_initiatives WHERE id = 1;

SELECT report_name, report_date FROM cultural_impact_reports WHERE report_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM diversity_initiatives;
SELECT id, initiative_name, start_date, end_date FROM diversity_initiatives WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT initiative_name, id, end_date FROM diversity_initiatives WHERE end_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT * FROM employee_diversity_feedback WHERE rating >= 4 ORDER BY rating DESC, submitted_date ASC;
SELECT report_name, report_date FROM cultural_impact_reports WHERE report_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';

SELECT initiative_name, impact_score FROM impact_of_diversity_initiatives ORDER BY impact_score DESC

SELECT response_id, survey_question, response_score FROM survey_responses WHERE response_date = '2022-01-01'
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM company_culture_metrics ORDER BY metric_date ASC

SELECT initiative_name, impact_score FROM impact_of_diversity_initiatives ORDER BY impact_score DESC
SELECT report_id, report_date FROM impact_of_diversity_initiatives WHERE impact_score > 50
SELECT * FROM employee_diversity_data WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY hire_date DESC

SELECT * FROM OrganizationalCulture ORDER BY satisfaction_score DESC;
SELECT employee_name, initiative_type, impact_score FROM DiversityInitiatives WHERE impact_score > 50;
SELECT report_title, publish_date, report_content FROM DiversityReports WHERE publish_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM DiversityInitiatives;
SELECT employee_name, initiative_type FROM DiversityInitiatives ORDER BY employee_name DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT initiative_type, impact_score FROM DiversityInitiatives WHERE impact_score > 50;
SELECT DI.employee_name, OC.satisfaction_score FROM DiversityInitiatives DI INNER JOIN OrganizationalCulture OC ON DI.employee_id = OC.employee_id;
SELECT DM.metric_name, DM.metric_value, DM.metric_date FROM DiversityMetrics DM WHERE DM.metric_value BETWEEN 100.00 AND 500.00 ORDER BY DM.metric_date DESC;
